configOptions.importQuery:
select 
t.id as tenant_id
, t.name as tenant_name
, DATE_TRUNC('month',e.created_at) as enrollment_creation_month
, COUNT(e.id) as new_enrollment_count
from "PC_FIVETRAN_DB"."PG_WMX_API_APP_SWAP_PUBLIC"."ENROLLMENTS" e
left join "PC_FIVETRAN_DB"."PG_WMX_API_APP_SWAP_PUBLIC"."CONTENT_PACKAGES" cp on cp.id = e.content_package_id
left join "PC_FIVETRAN_DB"."PG_WMX_API_APP_SWAP_PUBLIC"."TENANTS" t on cp.tenant_id = t.id
where 
e.created_at > date('2019-01-01')
GROUP BY t.id
, t.name
, DATE_TRUNC('month',e.created_at)

SELECT t.id as tenant_id
        , t.name as tenant_name
            ,DATE_TRUNC('month', e.nps_voted_at) as nps_survey_date
            ,sum(case when nps_course is not null then 1 else 0 end) as surveys_taken
            ,sum(case when nps_course in (9,10) then 1 else 0 end) as promoter_count
            ,sum(case when nps_course in (7,8) then 1 else 0 end) as passive_count
            ,sum(case when nps_course in (0,1,2,3,4,5,6) then 1 else 0 end) as detractor_count
        FROM "PC_FIVETRAN_DB"."PG_WMX_API_APP_SWAP_PUBLIC"."ENROLLMENTS" e
            LEFT JOIN "PC_FIVETRAN_DB"."PG_WMX_API_APP_SWAP_PUBLIC"."USERS" u
                ON e.user_id = u.id
        LEFT JOIN "PC_FIVETRAN_DB"."PG_WMX_API_APP_SWAP_PUBLIC"."TENANTS" t
            ON u.tenant_id = t.id
        WHERE u.email NOT LIKE '%benchprep%'
            and u.email NOT LIKE '%techment%'
            and u.email NOT LIKE '%smartscrolls%'
            and u.email NOT LIKE '%dtracks.in'
            and u.email <> 'sandragraver@gmail.com'
            and u.email <> 'lisaintheevening@gmail.com'
            and u.email <> 'hector.matias.torres@gmail.com'
            and u.email <> 'dmclauson@gmail.com'
            and e.created_at > dateadd(Year, -2, current_date())
            and DATE_TRUNC('month', e.nps_voted_at) IS NOT NULL
        GROUP BY t.id
            , t.name
            , DATE_TRUNC('month', e.nps_voted_at)
        ;

SELECT cpr.id as review_id
, DATE_TRUNC('month',cpr.created_at) as review_date
, cpr.rating as review_score 
, t.id as tenant_id
, t.name as tenant_name
from "PC_FIVETRAN_DB"."PG_WMX_API_APP_SWAP_PUBLIC"."CONTENT_PACKAGE_REVIEWS"  cpr
left join "PC_FIVETRAN_DB"."PG_WMX_API_APP_SWAP_PUBLIC"."USERS" u 
            on cpr.user_id = u.id
left join "PC_FIVETRAN_DB"."PG_WMX_API_APP_SWAP_PUBLIC"."TENANTS" t
    ON u.tenant_id = t.id
WHERE u.email NOT LIKE '%benchprep%'
    and u.email NOT LIKE '%techment%'
    and u.email NOT LIKE '%smartscrolls%'
    and u.email NOT LIKE '%dtracks.in'
    and u.email <> 'sandragraver@gmail.com'
    and u.email <> 'lisaintheevening@gmail.com'
    and u.email <> 'hector.matias.torres@gmail.com'
    and u.email <> 'dmclauson@gmail.com'
    and cpr.created_at > dateadd(Year, -2, current_date())
